{"tid":1939074,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有個經常被忽略嘅國家同香港有啲似，最後獨立左","createTime":"2020-03-23T02:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T05:54:32.000Z","uid":50588,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"51dc994f1f77f2653c87d088711155c197e43631","tid":1939074,"uid":50588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T02:51:01.000Z","msg":"睇到呢個post<br />\n塞爾維亞：只准中国人入境，其他人入境要坐三年監<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1938077\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1938077</a><br />\n<br />\n見咁多人屌緊Serbia<br />\n好想同大家講下其實前南斯拉夫入邊<br />\n有個國家成日比人忽略<br />\n但處景同香港有啲似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前應承左當地人要幫佢地spread開去<br />\n個國家就係波斯尼亞<br />\n<br />\n其實Serbia同支那冇大分別<br />\n佢地到而家都仲有Great Serbia呢個諗法<br />\n90年代打鳩過附近國家<br />\n受害最深之一就係波斯尼亞<br />\n當年佢地嘅惡行同Nazi差不多<br />\n種族屠殺，集中營，強姦乜都有<br />\n下邊係我其中一個睇到想喊嘅故事<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y1jRsQF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY1jRsQF.jpg&h=731ef4e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但國際上當當年嘅戰爭係內戰<br />\n一直任由波斯尼亞人比人屠殺，袖手旁觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但波斯尼亞嘅朋友好想同大家講：<br />\n我地係比人入侵！唔係內戰啊！<br />\n佢地都好無奈，奈何人微言輕，國際上根本冇人會show佢地<br />\n呢種感覺相信香港人都有感，而且我地處景已經比佢地好<br />\n<br />\n題外話，我係其中一個記念博物館見到啲咁嘅嘢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wCqAUEa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwCqAUEa.jpg&h=a50bf0ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話比佢知，佢即刻嬲到仆街<br />\n大家未去過嘅可能未有好深感受<br />\n但去過/有了解嘅真係會好撚嬲"},{"pid":"102dda51279dd6b864fe91fb7b195b12d9375e9a","tid":1939074,"uid":50588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T02:53:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2NVxcy2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2NVxcy2.jpg&h=6ef27b7d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0cc2680f369265fdc0f8631cab8f22d63b0c38b5","tid":1939074,"uid":208722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T02:55:01.000Z","msg":"當年有去薩拉熱窩睇條橋"},{"pid":"9f01ab444683affabf877c7561a1f313db6d9364","tid":1939074,"uid":50588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cc2680f369265fdc0f8631cab8f22d63b0c38b5","tid":1939074,"uid":208722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T02:55:01.000Z","msg":"當年有去薩拉熱窩睇條橋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T03:03:14.000Z","msg":"Sarajevo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f55e1a4c40f35f7c2d27dedf50c60640f83d0dd9","tid":1939074,"uid":50588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T03:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94640578559c8d3f333806954f6b877752a72fad","tid":1939074,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f55e1a4c40f35f7c2d27dedf50c60640f83d0dd9","tid":1939074,"uid":50588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T03:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T05:54:32.000Z","msg":"唔該支持聯署，用選民壓力逼候選人「埋枱」參加初選/協調！<br />\n<br />\n【重開行動Post】立會要初選， 「三不投」聯署<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1935886\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1935886</a>"}]}